Mart-Life Detox Clinic bụ ụlọ ọgwụ Myar nke oge a nke mbụ na Naịjirịa

Ụlọ ọgwụ ahụ bụ ụlọ ọgwụ Anti-age Spa na Wellness nakwa nke mbụ n'ụdị ya n'Afrịka. Medical Art Center (MART) guzobere maka enyemaka ọmụmụ, meghere Modern Mayr Medical Spa na Maryland, Lagos Steeti na mmekorita ya na Viva-Mayr Clinic na Austria. Ụlọ spa ahụ bụ ebe ahụike kachasị mma na ebe ntọhapụ nke nwere ụlọ ọgwụ na ahụkarị maka ọgwụgwọ na ịma mma
